{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_5_level_main_05-02_end","storyGroup":"main_5","storySort":4,"storyDependence":"main_5_level_main_05-02_beg","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"5-2","storyName":"有口难言","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"面对责难与质疑，陈给出了自己的回答，却被星熊看出了她的迟疑。\n不过无论如何，她至少知道自己在做什么。\n","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_main_05-02_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"main_05-02","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":2,"next":4,"characters":["罗德岛干员","陈","星熊","近卫局成员","诗怀雅"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"第二关（后）","id":0},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$newhope01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta3_181101/m_dia_newhope01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","crossfade":"1.5","delay":"0.5","id":1,"musicid":0},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_bg_bg_uptown_1.png","fadetime":"1","screenadapt":"coverall","id":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","fadetime":"1","focus":"2","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"在和他们正面冲突之前，我也没想到整合运动竟然会这么脆弱。","id":6,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"本以为他们给切城和其他小队造成了那么大麻烦，一定是非常强大的军事力量。","id":7,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"现在看来，任务简报上的资料没什么大问题，整合运动的实力确实也就那样。对整合运动阴谋的了解不足才是任务的难点。","id":8,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":9},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"不要大意。整合运动的最大优势，本就在于出乎所有人的意料。","id":10,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"渗透、突然袭击、动用特殊力量攻坚，都是他们的常用手段。我们并不清楚他们隐藏了什么。","id":11,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":12},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"我明白，毕竟这么强盛的龙门和那么庞大的切尔诺伯格，都已经遭到了整合运动的侵袭。也许他们的数量真的超乎想象吧。","id":13,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"不过，陈长官，之前的任务中，阿米娅是和近卫局一同行动的，你们不是一起去侦查切城废城了吗，阿米娅他们怎么还没归队？","id":14,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":15},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"......抱歉。","id":16,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"1","id":17},{"type":"dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"（老陈......）","id":18,"figure":"char_136_hsguma_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"我们与阿米娅的小队失散了。我们没法跟他们汇合，情况紧急，我们只能先行离开。","id":20,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"你的意思是，你们近卫局把阿米娅和Dr.{@nickname}就这样留在了废城？","id":22,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":23},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"是。","id":24,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"也就是说他们现在生死不明？","id":26,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"不，陈长官......","id":27,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"不。即使你们是龙门近卫局也不能这样做。即使是龙门近卫局，也不应该、更不能抛弃合作伙伴。","id":28,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":29},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"这是我的失职。我的任务是优先维护龙门的安全，作出了这个判断的是我。","id":30,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":31},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"知道负责人又能怎样......不用再说下去了，龙门的警官，这件事已经没什么好说的了。","id":32,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"也是。是啊，我其实很清楚你们对感染者的态度。","id":33,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"我不是这个意思——","id":35,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"2","id":36},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"你需要多少干员？会有干员愿意协助你的，尽管我不会。","id":37,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"我们也有任务。帮助龙门战胜整合运动同样也是我们的任务。","id":38,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛干员","text":"只不过我会和罗德岛的小队自己去做。记好我们的识别码，长官。请不要误伤合作伙伴，哪怕他们是感染者。","id":39,"figure":"avg_npc_012"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_012","focus":"1","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"......我知道了。","id":41,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"如果有愿意和近卫局一起行动的，可以向我报到。","id":42,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"——不必勉强自己。","id":43,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",0]},{"type":"dialog","id":44},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":45},{"type":"delay","time":"0.3","id":46},{"type":"character","id":47},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":48},{"type":"character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","focus":"1","id":49},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":50},{"type":"dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"你和诗怀雅刚才那出，难道不是为了加强和罗德岛之间的合作吗？","id":51,"figure":"char_136_hsguma_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"怎么到了罗德岛这边，你又临阵变卦，不按说好的来？","id":52,"figure":"char_136_hsguma_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#6","focus":"2","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"你弄错了，星熊。我没这个打算。","id":54,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#6","focus":"1","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"可能吧。至少我更乐意看你说实话。你的表情也比刚才坦然多了。","id":56,"figure":"char_136_hsguma_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"不过确实，把我放在他那个位置，我一样会很恼火。你得庆幸那个罗德岛的战士还挺好说话。","id":57,"figure":"char_136_hsguma_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"这么说吧，我知道时间紧迫，可我也弄不明白——为什么你要把阿米娅他们那么干脆地留在废城？","id":58,"figure":"char_136_hsguma_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"2","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"不确定因素太多了。","id":60,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"废城的地况不适合近卫局战斗，我们也很难估计废城内整合运动的实力。我们的队伍不能承担这种风险。","id":61,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"1","id":62},{"type":"dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"这说服不了我。","id":63,"figure":"char_136_hsguma_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"2","id":64},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"......星熊，我们的行动是被规划好的。","id":65,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"1","id":66},{"type":"dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"命令就是命令，我会服从。但你该亲自和我说，而不是让我等到诗怀雅来告知我。","id":67,"figure":"char_136_hsguma_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"2","id":68},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"在当今事态成真之前，命令的具体内容是机密的。","id":69,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"1","id":70},{"type":"dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"所以是魏先生亲自下的命令。","id":71,"figure":"char_136_hsguma_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"2","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"你可以随便猜测。","id":73,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"1","id":74},{"type":"dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"即使现在是，我也不知道你们的具体目标，在龙门没什么人能让近卫局做到这步。","id":75,"figure":"char_136_hsguma_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"只可能是这样。","id":76,"figure":"char_136_hsguma_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"我确实很佩服魏先生。但我不会敬重他，今天发生的一切就是原因之一。","id":77,"figure":"char_136_hsguma_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"2","id":78},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"这一切都是必要的。","id":79,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"1","id":80},{"type":"dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"你在说服你自己。","id":81,"figure":"char_136_hsguma_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"唉，老陈，你要么是想得太多，要么是连自己都说服不了。","id":82,"figure":"char_136_hsguma_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"2","id":83},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"可能吧。","id":84,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"帮我接诗怀雅。","id":86,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","name2":"char_015_lmg","focus":"2","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"近卫局成员","text":"明白。","id":88,"figure":"char_015_lmg"},{"type":"dialog","id":89},{"type":"character","id":90},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","volume":"0.4","id":91},{"type":"charactercutin","widgetID":"1","name":"char_308_swire_1#5","style":"cutin","fadestyle":"horiz_expand_center","fadetime":"0.5","offsetx":"-300","width":"200","block":"true","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诗怀雅","text":"喂？","id":93},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"2","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"诗怀雅，我们已经离开了罗德岛，你那边可以开始了。","id":95,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"1","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诗怀雅","text":"刚才骂我骂得挺舒服的，嗯？","id":97,"figure":"char_empty"},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"2","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"我们关系很差，但没差到那个地步。我是有点虚张声势。","id":99,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"1","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诗怀雅","text":"但我可不是，我骂爽了。","id":101,"figure":"char_empty"},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"char_010_chen_1#4","focus":"2","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"你这家伙......","id":103,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"char_010_chen_1#4","focus":"1","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诗怀雅","text":"行，行。真奇怪，我们都只知道自己的任务，却一点也不知道对方的。","id":105,"figure":"char_empty"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诗怀雅","text":"还有，我听说了，你为什么不希望罗德岛插手？这是某种程度的赎罪吗？","id":106,"figure":"char_empty"},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"2","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"我相信罗德岛的能力，也相信阿米娅和Dr.{@nickname}。","id":108,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"所以我不想让他们介入现在的情况，他们只会是不确定的因素。","id":109,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"甚至是那个凯尔希。她绝不会按我们的规划行事。","id":110,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"1","id":111},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诗怀雅","text":"我没见过那家伙。","id":112,"figure":"char_empty"},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"2","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"没必要见了。有点像你祖父，而且不用每天戴着呼吸机。","id":114,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"1","id":115},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诗怀雅","text":"啊。","id":116,"figure":"char_empty"},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"2","id":117},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"各自开工吧。不过我要先去找个人。","id":118,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"1","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"诗怀雅","text":"随你。记得看时间。","id":120,"figure":"char_empty"},{"type":"dialog","id":121},{"type":"character","id":122},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","volume":"0.4","id":123},{"type":"charactercutin","widgetID":"1","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":124},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#1","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"星熊，走吧。","id":126,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"1","id":127},{"type":"dialogue","name":"星熊","text":"去哪？","id":128,"figure":"char_136_hsguma_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_136_hsguma","name2":"char_010_chen_1#1","focus":"2","id":129},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"木禾仓库。","id":130,"figure":["char_010_chen_1",0]},{"type":"delay","time":"0.3","id":131},{"type":"dialog","id":132},{"type":"blocker","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":133},{"type":"image","id":134}],"characters":["罗德岛干员","陈","星熊","近卫局成员","诗怀雅"]}